.card.mb-3
  .card-header My Patreon Benefits
  - pledge_cents = current_user.patreon.try(:pledge_cents) || 0
  .list-group
    .list-group-item
      .d-flex.w-100.justify-content-between
        - if current_user.bronze_patron?
          h5.mb1
            span.text-success> ✓
            ' No Ads
          i.btn.btn-outline-light.disabled Complete!
        - else
          h5.mb1
            span.text-danger> ✗
            ' No Ads
          a.btn.btn-outline-patreon href=patreon_url(checkout: :bronze)
            => icon('fab', 'patreon')
            ' Subscribe
      p.mb-1
        ' Make the ad at the top of the page go away, but without feeling guilty about it. Comes with a
        ' #{user_badge(current_user, override: :standard)} → #{user_badge(current_user, override: :silver)} username
        ' upgrade.
    .list-group-item
      .d-flex.w-100.justify-content-between
        - if current_user.silver_patron?
          h5.mb1
            span.text-success> ✓
            ' PB Predictions
          i.btn.btn-outline-light.disabled Complete!
        - else
          h5.mb1
            span.text-danger> ✗
            ' PB Predictions
          a.btn.btn-outline-patreon href=patreon_url(checkout: :silver)
            => icon('fab', 'patreon')
            ' Subscribe
      p.mb-1
        ' No ads, and predict how many hours of attempts you need to hit specific PBs (as a graph). Comes with a
        ' #{user_badge(current_user, override: :silver)} → #{user_badge(current_user, override: :gold)}
        ' username upgrade.
    .list-group-item
      .d-flex.w-100.justify-content-between
        - if current_user.gold_patron?
          h5.mb1
            span.text-success> ✓
            ' Permalink Redirectors
          i: a.btn.btn-outline-light.disabled href=tools_path Complete!
        - else
          h5.mb1
            span.text-danger> ✗
            ' Permalink Redirectors
          a.btn.btn-outline-patreon href=patreon_url(checkout: :gold)
            => icon('fab', 'patreon')
            ' Subscribe
      p.mb-1
        ' No ads, get PB predictions, and get special static links that always redirect to your current PB, even when it
        ' improves.
  .card-footer
    p All tiers also put you in the footer of the site! 😍 See Patreon for how much the site costs to run.
